{"tid":530132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你搵到生活既意義未？","createTime":"2018-01-15T13:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T17:52:17.000Z","uid":92065,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f76dbc2a29d5fdc7624815dcf7bbf79294470e","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"人生每一個階段都追尋緊某啲意義<br />\n或者可以叫做目的<br />\n小學希望入好中學<br />\n中學希望可以升到大學<br />\n大學希望可以過三爆四<br />\n但一入左社大之後好似突然冇目的咁<br />\n翻緊份工又冇乜意義<br />\n好冇動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有類似感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下你地既意義啟發下我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d49144cd9fa7b6b04f5eb12ff50ee55eef01ed","tid":530132,"uid":162043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"退休咪係目的囉"},{"pid":"d8809ab4537807d6c960e2cc059164494f17cf60","tid":530132,"uid":124107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5676b02551e2200cea4a5333489ae8e1254bde98","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d9d49144cd9fa7b6b04f5eb12ff50ee55eef01ed","tid":530132,"uid":162043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"退休咪係目的囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"我都知退休係工作既目的<br />\n但廿幾歲就以退休做目的好冇實感<br />\n我係咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f2152a78cb6df5a98dfcc4d3d60b2eb2cf91b4","tid":530