faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知無可能咁順利，但叫做set左個目標。"},{"pid":"7e08613fab4e95b8cc03f1114012b46bdd23dc4d","tid":530132,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e243e61d14967b343c53875a9d0d8944ee3e6bd","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ecd7f632decac009948eb334075b805a73236f8","tid":530132,"uid":43051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"日日諗 抑鬱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"我頭先真係有睇過下抑鬱既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"有過抑鬱焦慮先知做返正常人返工放工幾幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e5437602c820572ac790cbd4e1a12c01ed40eb","tid":530132,"uid":77956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/16/003430_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F003430_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=3126b0e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"533364cf838f0e3aa6b6b18ebb247b860897cc69","tid":530132,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0f76dbc2a29d5fdc7624815dcf7bbf79294470e","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:05:07.000Z","msg":"人生每一個階段都追尋緊某啲意義<br />\n或者可以叫做目的<br />\n小學希望入好中學<br />\n中學希望可以升到大學<br />\n大學希望可以過三爆四<br />\n但一入左社大之後好似突然冇目的咁<br />\n翻緊份工又冇乜意義<br />\n好冇動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲有類似感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分享下你地既意義啟發下我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"我人生最大意義就係要完成由底層變為頂層依一個一般人認為冇乜可能嘅任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能係我自己嘅心理問題，但係果種一直畀人欺壓嘅感受真係忍無可忍。"},{"pid":"4edf57bf630617a5251d50c104508b5cc5c30023","tid":530132,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f17f396fa32220f5fec2f96c54a4a96a06baf0ea","tid":530132,"uid":156664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"404 not found"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"500 Internal Server Error<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bc733c6132fbc46fda28ed4e28319eaa69cfd2","tid":530132,"uid":70695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b616aee2c25d4b7b2ccc1df881f1f078dad28b11","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f17f396fa32220f5fec2f96c54a4a96a06baf0ea","tid":530132,"uid":156664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"404 not found"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"Not found 真係唔知點咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"same"},{"pid":"7929bb3951dcdd1a8e1f78a3315bd310efc6b04c","tid":530132,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T16:48:52.000Z","msg":"份工朝10晚5半間中先忙 <br />\n一日用1/4時間就可以做晒野<br />\n人工還好有2字頭<br />\n好多同齡朋友叫入政府同轉工<br />\n因為份工太hea太得閒<br />\n但呢份工 可以兼顧到好多野<br />\n屋企啲寵物 自己既興趣 家人 朋友 女朋友<br />\n同埋有番個生活質素 <br />\n放工唔會攰到運動都做唔到<br />\n覺得咁樣既生活 比起忙足9個鐘有意義啲"},{"pid":"5d514518e6f427636cb71436bd263ee934d53817","tid":530132,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faf09993a0dfe2086906ebee18a36e55816f4faa","tid":530132,"uid":64696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"